            <title>[FLINK-2813] Document off-heap configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2813</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Managed memory can be allocated off-heap by setting &lt;tt&gt;taskmanager.memory.off-heap&lt;/tt&gt; to true. The heap memory will be adjusted according to the size of the off-heap memory. The size of the off-heap memory, is controlled using the &lt;tt&gt;taskmanager.memory.fraction&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;taskmanager.memory.size&lt;/tt&gt; parameter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
